title: O'Neill CWC New Zealand 11 - Day 4 HL
description: Day 4 was ruled by the top seeds. The event's top seed, Adam Melling (AUS), was the first surfer to move through to Round of 12. The event remained at 'The Pipe' on Midway Beach for the second consecutive day.
